      "content": "i know about the numbers, i've seen them all. it's not that i need a hotline, it's just that nobody understands how hollow this actually feels. it’s like i’ve run out of ways to fix things. i look at my life and there's nothing left to build on. it’s not even sadness anymore, it’s just this deep, permanent emptiness. i'm just so done with the cycle of trying and failing.",
